        <Parent_String>woods (plant communities) [300132451], forests (plant communities) [300387598], plant communities (natural) [300132439], vegetation [300266061], natural landscapes [300132294], landscapes (environments) [300008626], Settlements and Landscapes (hierarchy name) [300008346], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
